The forces of the giant strike are gathering
The League Unions and the National Federation of Workers&#39; Commissions will constitute a strike commission on Friday to coordinate the strike on Monday that will last indefinitely.
A protest rally will be held on Saturday, while on Monday - the day the final vote on the public health law will be held - the work stoppage will begin.
This action will surely cause great difficulties in transport, since the railway traffic will be completely stopped and until 1 pm the workers of the Public Transport Company of Budapest will also be on strike.
